```md
# Advyser V1 — Component Checklist (shadcn-style)
Goal: enumerate UI components needed per screen so you can build quickly and consistently.

Assumptions:
- Web app (Next.js) + responsive design
- shadcn/ui primitives + minimal custom components
- Shared design tokens: spacing, typography, badges

---

## Shared UI Kit (build once)

### Layout
- AppShell
  - PublicHeader
  - ConsumerHeader
  - AdvisorHeader
  - AdminHeader
  - Footer
- PageContainer (max width + responsive padding)
- TwoColumnLayout (left rail + main content)
- TabsLayout (tabbed sections)

### Inputs
- TextInput
- TextArea
- Select
- MultiSelect (tag picker)
- RadioGroup (Online/In-person/Either)
- Checkbox
- ToggleSwitch
- DatePicker (optional V1)
- FileUploader (drag/drop + progress)
- OTPInput (phone verification)

### Display
- Card
- Avatar
- Badge (Verified, Licence Verified, Fast Responder, New)
- Chip/Tag
- Tooltip
- Alert (info/warn/error)
- Skeleton (loading)
- EmptyState (icon + copy + CTA)
- ProgressStepper (status timeline)
- Table (admin, dashboard lists)
- Pagination / InfiniteScroll

### Actions
- Button (primary/secondary/destructive)
- DropdownMenu (sort, status)
- Dialog/Modal (confirmations, filters on mobile)
- Drawer/Sheet (mobile filters)
- Toast (success/failure)

### Messaging
- ConversationThread
- MessageBubble (sender/receiver)
- MessageComposer (textarea + attachments + templates dropdown)
- AttachmentList (with preview icons)

### Admin
- AdminDetailPanel (split view)
- EvidenceViewer (file list + preview link)
- RegisterLinkList (quick links)

---

# Screen-by-Screen Components

## Screen 1 — Home
**Sections**
- HeroSection
- SearchModule
- CategoryTiles
- TrustRow

**Components**
- PublicHeader, Footer
- HeroSection:
  - H1, Paragraph
- SearchModule:
  - Select (Advisor Type)
  - LocationAutocompleteInput (suburb/postcode)
  - Select (Radius)
  - Button (Search)
  - HelperText
- CategoryTiles:
  - CardGrid (4)
  - CategoryCard (icon, label, CTA)
- TrustRow:
  - IconTextRow items (3)

**States**
- Location search loading (spinner)
- Invalid location (Alert)

---

## Screen 2 — Search Results
**Sections**
- ResultsHeader (summary + sort)
- FiltersPanel (desktop) / FiltersDrawer (mobile)
- ResultsList
- Pagination

**Components**
- PublicHeader, Footer
- ResultsHeader:
  - Breadcrumb
  - ResultsSummaryText
  - SortDropdown (DropdownMenu + Select)
- FiltersPanel:
  - FilterGroup components:
    - AdvisorTypeMultiSelect
    - ServiceModePills (RadioGroup)
    - SpecialtyMultiSelect
    - FeeModelMultiSelect
    - ToggleSwitch (Verified only)
    - ToggleSwitch (Taking new clients)
    - ToggleSwitch (Openings in 7 days)
    - LanguageMultiSelect
  - ClearFiltersButton
- FiltersDrawer (mobile):
  - Drawer/Sheet
  - ApplyFiltersButton
- ResultsList:
  - ListingCard (reusable)
- ListingCard:
  - Avatar
  - Title (Name/Business)
  - BadgesRow
  - MetaLine (type + location + distance)
  - TagRow (specialties)
  - PriceLine
  - Snippet
  - CTA Button "View profile"
  - Secondary Button "Request intro"
  - ExplainabilityLine (Tooltip optional)
- Skeleton list
- EmptyState

**States**
- Loading results (Skeleton)
- No results (EmptyState + clear)
- Partial data (price unknown → show "Pricing not listed")

---

## Screen 3 — Advisor Profile
**Sections**
- ProfileHero
- ProfileTabs: Overview | Services & Pricing | Credentials | Reviews
- Sticky CTA (mobile)

**Components**
- PublicHeader, Footer
- ProfileHero:
  - Avatar/Logo
  - Name/Business
  - BadgesRow
  - Meta (type, location, modes)
  - Primary CTA Button (Request intro)
  - Secondary CTA (Message) gated by login
  - DisclaimerAlert (AU boundary)
- Tabs:
  - Tabs component
- OverviewTab:
  - Card sections: Who I help, What we do, Specialties (TagRow), Areas (list)
- ServicesTab:
  - ServiceOfferingCard list:
    - Title
    - PriceText
    - IncludedList (bullets)
- CredentialsTab:
  - CredentialsTable:
    - Type, Number, State, Verified badge, Verified date tooltip
- ReviewsTab:
  - RatingSummary (stars + count)
  - ReviewCard list
  - Tooltip "Verified engagements only"
- Inactive listing alert

**States**
- Unclaimed listing: show "Claim this business" CTA (links to Screen 7)
- Missing reviews: EmptyState "No reviews yet"

---

## Screen 4 — Request Intro
**Sections**
- Form: Needs help | Situation | Logistics | Consent
- Success panel

**Components**
- PublicHeader, Footer
- FormCard
- Select (Primary goal)
- MultiSelect (Specialties)
- TextArea (Situation)
- RadioGroup (Meeting mode)
- LocationInput (prefilled)
- Select (Timeline)
- Select (Budget range optional)
- FileUploader (optional docs)
- Checkbox (Consent)
- Buttons: Send request, Save draft (optional)
- InlineValidationMessages
- SuccessAlert (Request sent)
- CTA: Go to My Requests

**States**
- Not logged in → intercept with Modal: "Create account to send request"
- File upload error → Toast + inline message

---

## Screen 5 — Sign up / Login
**Sections**
- AuthCard with tabs

**Components**
- PublicHeader, Footer
- AuthCard
- Tabs (Sign up / Login)
- TextInput (Email)
- PasswordInput
- PhoneInput (optional)
- Checkbox (Terms)
- Button submit
- Link "Forgot password"
- EmailVerificationNotice (alert)

**States**
- Incorrect login → Alert
- Rate-limited → Alert "Try again later"

---

## Screen 6 — Consumer Dashboard (My Requests)
**Sections**
- Tabs: My Requests | Messages | Settings
- RequestsList
- RequestDetail view (subpage)

**Components**
- ConsumerHeader
- Tabs
- RequestsTable (or Cards on mobile)
  - columns: Advisor/Business, Type, StatusChip, LastUpdated, CTA View
- EmptyState
- RequestDetail:
  - SummaryCard (what user submitted)
  - StatusTimeline (ProgressStepper)
  - ConversationThread
  - MessageComposer
  - AttachmentList

**States**
- New message indicator badge
- Archived request hidden by default (toggle "Show archived")

---

## Screen 7 — Claim Business / Join
**Sections**
- BusinessSearch + ClaimFlow wizard

**Components**
- PublicHeader or AdvisorHeader (depending on entry)
- Stepper/Wizard (3–4 steps)
- BusinessSearchInput (typeahead)
- Button "My business isn’t listed" (Create business modal)
- ClaimForm:
  - TextInput (Full name)
  - Select (Role: Owner/Staff)
  - TextInput (Work email)
  - PhoneInput + OTP flow:
    - Button "Send code"
    - OTPInput
- ProofOfControlSelector (RadioGroup):
  - Phone OTP to business phone
  - Email domain verify
  - Website code verify
- CredentialsSection (conditional by advisor type):
  - Select (Advisor Type)
  - TextInput(s) for licence numbers
  - FileUploader (evidence)
- Submit button
- StatusPanel:
  - Pending / Needs more info / Approved / Denied

**States**
- Business not found → "Create listing" flow
- OTP failed → inline error
- Pending review → disable edits or allow “update claim” based on policy

---

## Screen 8 — Advisor Dashboard (Lead Inbox)
**Sections**
- KPI strip
- Lead pipeline (filter/status)
- Lead list

**Components**
- AdvisorHeader
- KPIStatCards (New, Response time, Acceptance rate)
- StatusFilterPills (New/Contacted/Booked/Converted/Declined/Closed)
- LeadsTable/Cards:
  - ClientLabel
  - GoalTag
  - Location
  - Submitted date
  - StatusChip
  - Last message
  - CTA Open
- Row quick actions:
  - Accept (Button)
  - Decline (Button destructive)
  - Request more info (Dropdown templates)
- EmptyState with tips + CTA "Complete profile"

**States**
- Accept/decline confirmation Dialog
- Decline requires reason Modal

---

## Screen 9 — Lead Detail (Advisor)
**Sections**
- Top action bar
- Two-column: Client brief | Messages
- Internal notes panel
- (Optional) Copilot entry point

**Components**
- AdvisorHeader
- TopActionBar:
  - StatusDropdown
  - Buttons: Accept / Decline / Mark booked / Archive
- ClientBriefCard:
  - Goal
  - Situation text
  - Logistics chips
  - DocumentsList
  - MissingInfoChecklist (manual V1)
- ConversationThread
- MessageComposer:
  - TemplatesDropdown (Request docs, Next steps, Booking)
  - File attach
- NotesTimeline:
  - NoteCard list
  - AddNote composer
- CreateClientWorkspaceBanner:
  - "Accepting creates a client workspace and enables Copilot."
- BookingMiniPanel (optional):
  - Proposed time slots or link out

**States**
- Lead not accepted yet → show “Accept to enable Copilot”
- Attachment preview fails → graceful fallback

---

## Screen 10 — Admin Console
**Sections**
- Tabs: Claims | Credentials | Reviews | Listings | Reports
- Table list + DetailPanel split view

**Components**
- AdminHeader
- Tabs
- AdminTable (filter + search)
- DetailPanel (split view)
- ClaimDetail:
  - BusinessSnapshotCard
  - ABNVerificationCard
  - ClaimantIdentityCard
  - EvidenceViewer (files)
  - RegisterLinkList
  - Actions: Approve / Needs more info / Deny
  - DenyReasonSelect + LockoutToggle
- CredentialsQueue:
  - CredentialRow + quick verify actions
- ReviewsQueue:
  - ReviewCard + Approve/Reject/Hide buttons
- ReportsQueue:
  - ReportCard + actions (warn/suspend/request info)

**States**
- Bulk actions (optional)
- Audit trail viewer (later)

---

# Reusable Custom Components (build early)

## 1) LocationAutocompleteInput
- Data: AU suburb/postcode dataset
- Output: {suburb, postcode, state, lat, lng}
- Supports "Online only" mode

## 2) ListingCard (search + related sections)
- Accepts:
  - name, business
  - badges[]
  - specialties[]
  - distance_km?
  - price_text?
  - explainability_reason?

## 3) VerificationBadge + Tooltip
- Variants:
  - Basic Verified
  - Licence Verified
- Tooltip content:
  - "Verified on YYYY-MM-DD"
  - "Source: Register/Documentation"

## 4) StatusTimeline (Lead)
- Stages:
  - Submitted → Accepted → Booked → Completed
- Works for consumer and advisor views

## 5) FileUploader + AttachmentList
- File types: pdf/docx/jpg/png/txt
- Show: filename, size, upload status
- Preview link

## 6) TemplatesDropdown (Messaging)
- Templates scoped by advisor type:
  - Request more info
  - Document checklist
  - Next steps
  - Booking prompt

---

# Minimum Design Copy Set (AU-safe)

## Site-wide disclaimer (footer)
"Advyser connects you with financial and property professionals. Information on this site is general and not personal advice."

## Request Intro consent
"I understand Advyser connects me with an advisor and does not provide personal advice."

## Advisor dashboard banner (Copilot)
"Copilot creates drafts for your review. You remain responsible for advice and client communications."

---

# Done-Definition Checklist (UI)
- All forms have validation + error copy
- All list pages have loading + empty states
- All destructive actions confirm (decline, archive, deny claim)
- All verification info has tooltip showing verified date/source
- Mobile filter drawer works on Search Results
